gin":true,"scopedCSS":"##scoped .layout__content{\npadding-top:0px !important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":0,"lineMargin":0,"backgroundColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","backgroundPosition":"middle","backgroundFilter":"none","backdropIntensity":50,"parallax":false,"backgroundPattern":false,"overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle"}},"16510493383aef7fc3":{"type":"section__faq","blocks":{"c70f0641-b284-4e15-8035-d1376577615a":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>Specifications Of Halo Mattress Topper<\/p>","answer":"<ul><li>- Outer fabric: 300gsm Poly (knitted\/Double Jacquard)<br\/><\/li><li>- Filling: 4cm 45D visco open-cell memory foam<\/li><li>- Packaging: Rolled and boxed<\/li><\/ul>"}},"accordion_qnFaHW":{"type":"accordion","disabled":true,"settings":{"question":"<p>How to build bed frame? (PDF Instruction)<\/p>","answer":"<p>You can find a detailed instruction about how to assembly the bed frame <a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0635\/4432\/8438\/files\/17Y_Instruction_manual.pdf?v=1709033581\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"PDF instruction\">using this link<\/a>.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["c70f0641-b284-4e15-8035-d1376577615a","accordion_qnFaHW"],"settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":true,"scopedCSS":"","height":0,"padding":20,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"#ffffff","backgroundPosition":"middle","backgroundFilter":"none","backdropIntensity":50,"parallax":false,"backgroundPattern":false,"overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","maxContentWidth":100,"faqid":"","heading":"Comfort is in the detail","headingColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","subheading":"","subheadingColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","subheadingPosition":"above","headingAlignment":"center","textContent":""}},"1650400037410d6fbc":{"type":"section__faq","blocks":{"cd3e7f05-b1cc-4cba-92e7-cdf0d8753331":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>Can the Halo Topper revitalise an older mattress?<\/p>","answer":"<p>Absolutely! The REM-Fit Halo Topper is an excellent solution for revitalising an older mattress. Its 4cm open-cell visco memory foam adapts to your body’s contours, adding a layer of luxurious comfort and support that can breathe new life into your existing mattress.<\/p>"}},"accordion_4hzGz3":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>Can I use the Halo Topper with my brand-new REM-Fit mattress?<\/p><p><\/p>","answer":"<p>Absolutely, the Halo Topper can enhance even a brand-new REM-Fit mattress. While your new mattress already offers excellent support and comfort, adding the Halo Topper can take it to the next level of luxury. The topper provides an additional layer of plush comfort with its 4cm open-cell visco memory foam, adapting perfectly to your body’s contours. It’s an ideal choice if you’re looking to customize the feel of your new mattress for an even more personalized and indulgent sleep experience.<\/p>"}},"accordion_HmUwXB":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>Will the Halo Topper stay in place on my mattress?<\/p>","answer":"<p>The REM-Fit Halo Topper is designed with elastic straps that securely attach to your mattress, ensuring it stays firmly in place. You can sleep soundly without worrying about the topper shifting or bunching up during the night.<\/p>"}},"accordion_wF8jeq":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>How does the mesh border improve breathability?<\/p>","answer":"<p>The mesh border of the Halo Topper allows for superior airflow, further enhancing the topper's breathability. This feature, often overlooked in other toppers, helps keep you cool and comfortable, especially in warmer weather or for those who tend to sleep hot.<\/p>"}},"67e26df9-71b5-4fba-802f-11ff8e66920a":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>Is the cover of the Halo Topper removable and washable?<\/p>","answer":"<p>Yes, the Halo Topper features a removable cover that can be easily unzipped and machine washed. This makes it simple to maintain a fresh and hygienic sleep environment.<\/p>"}},"e295a5c8-ba15-4bd9-9399-ddd3fa1a54ea":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>What makes the Re-Ax cover special?<\/p>","answer":"<p>The Re-Ax cover on the Halo Topper is specially designed to enhance breathability. It helps regulate your body temperature by promoting airflow, ensuring you stay cool and comfortable throughout the night.<\/p>"}},"1b3add3b-1d0c-496e-8b7c-012119c467c5":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>What is the delivery process like?<\/p>","answer":"<p>The Halo Topper is rolled and boxed for convenience, making it easy to transport and set up. It’s delivered with 1-3 day service via DPD, so you can start enjoying enhanced comfort almost immediately. Plus, it comes with a 30-night sleep trial and a 10-year guarantee for your peace of mind.<\/p>"}},"accordion_XMeqXm":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"question":"<p>What if I'm not satisfied with the Halo Topper?<\/p>","answer":"<p>We’re confident you’ll love the Halo Topper, but if for any reason it doesn’t meet your expectations, you can take advantage of our 30-night sleep trial. If you're not satisfied, you can return it for a full refund within this period.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["cd3e7f05-b1cc-4cba-92e7-cdf0d8753331","accordion_4hzGz3","accordion_HmUwXB","accordion_wF8jeq","67e26df9-71b5-4fba-802f-11ff8e66920a","e295a5c8-ba15-4bd9-9399-ddd3fa1a54ea","1b3add3b-1d0c-496e-8b7c-012119c467c5","accordion_XMeqXm"],"settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":true,"scopedCSS":"","height":0,"padding":20,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"#ecf7fd","backgroundPosition":"middle","backgroundFilter":"none","backdropIntensity":50,"parallax":false,"backgroundPattern":false,"overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAl